            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212035447/image_1212035447.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bear Market\" data-id=\"1212035447\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"4098px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212035447/image_1212035447.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212035447/image_1212035447.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212035447/image_1212035447.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212035447/image_1212035447.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212035447/image_1212035447.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212035447/image_1212035447.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212035447/image_1212035447.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212035447/image_1212035447.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">DNY59</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The energy sector has been struggling lately due to plunging oil prices. For example, the WTI crude oil spot price has declined by about 15% since mid-January, bringing many blue-chip energy stocks lower with it.</p> <p></p> <p>These include the likes</p>",
